OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJohn Lewis, Tesco and Lidl 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftone down Christmas ads    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Christmas adverts have started on TV - 
OL,6, and as ever, many conjure up           
OL,7, sentimentality, nostalgia and joy.     
OL,9,FBut as the cost of living soars, some  
OL,10,Fretailers have opted for a more muted  
OL,11,Fapproach to their campaigns this year. 
OL,13,FJohn Lewis said its advert, featuring a
OL,14,Ffoster family, was less about buying   
OL,15,Fthings and more about kindness.        
OL,17,FBut some retail experts warned scenes  
OL,18,Fof bountiful buffets in other ads were 
OL,19,Fstill out of touch as families struggle
OL,20,Fwith rising prices.                    
